{"cacheTime": "undefined", "baseUrl": "https://kater.me/d/62880", "title": "祕笈：全站搜尋篩選功能", "content": [{"author": "天涯之外", "body": "\n<p>\n 前情提要：\n <a href=\"https://kater.me/d/62837\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">\n 祕笈：全站搜尋篩選作者\n </a>\n</p>\n<hr/>\n<p>\n 還是放在一起全部說一次好了。\n </p>\n<p>\n Flarum 原生搜尋提供四種篩選，分別是：\n </p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n 仍有未讀樓層的文章：\n <pre data-hljs=\"\"><code class=\"language-text\"> is:unread</code></pre>\n<script>\n if(\"undefined\"!==typeof hljs)hljs._ha();else if(\"undefined\"===typeof hljsLoading){hljsLoading=1;var a=document.getElementsByTagName(\"head\")[0],e=document.createElement(\"link\");e.type=\"text/css\";e.rel=\"stylesheet\";e.href=\"//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/highlight.js/9.7.0/styles/default.min.css\";a.appendChild(e);e=document.createElement(\"script\");e.type=\"text/javascript\";e.onload=function(){var d={},f=0;hljs._hb=function(b){b.removeAttribute(\"data-hljs\");var c=b.innerHTML;c in d?b.innerHTML=d[c]:(7<++f&&(d={},f=0),hljs.highlightBlock(b.firstChild),d[c]=b.innerHTML)};hljs._ha=function(){for(var b=document.querySelectorAll(\"pre[data-hljs]\"),c=b.length;0<c;)hljs._hb(b.item(--c))};hljs._ha()};e.async=!0;e.src=\"//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/highlight.js/9.7.0/highlight.min.js\";a.appendChild(e)}\n </script>\n</li>\n<li>\n 只顯示隱藏文章（刪除文章）：\n <pre data-hljs=\"\"><code class=\"language-text\"> is:hidden</code></pre>\n<script>\n if(\"undefined\"!==typeof hljs)hljs._ha();else if(\"undefined\"===typeof hljsLoading){hljsLoading=1;var a=document.getElementsByTagName(\"head\")[0],e=document.createElement(\"link\");e.type=\"text/css\";e.rel=\"stylesheet\";e.href=\"//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/highlight.js/9.7.0/styles/default.min.css\";a.appendChild(e);e=document.createElement(\"script\");e.type=\"text/javascript\";e.onload=function(){var d={},f=0;hljs._hb=function(b){b.removeAttribute(\"data-hljs\");var c=b.innerHTML;c in d?b.innerHTML=d[c]:(7<++f&&(d={},f=0),hljs.highlightBlock(b.firstChild),d[c]=b.innerHTML)};hljs._ha=function(){for(var b=document.querySelectorAll(\"pre[data-hljs]\"),c=b.length;0<c;)hljs._hb(b.item(--c))};hljs._ha()};e.async=!0;e.src=\"//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/highlight.js/9.7.0/highlight.min.js\";a.appendChild(e)}\n </script>\n</li>\n<li>\n 篩選文章作者：\n <pre data-hljs=\"\"><code class=\"language-text\"> author:&lt;使用者暱稱&gt;</code></pre>\n<script>\n if(\"undefined\"!==typeof hljs)hljs._ha();else if(\"undefined\"===typeof hljsLoading){hljsLoading=1;var a=document.getElementsByTagName(\"head\")[0],e=document.createElement(\"link\");e.type=\"text/css\";e.rel=\"stylesheet\";e.href=\"//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/highlight.js/9.7.0/styles/default.min.css\";a.appendChild(e);e=document.createElement(\"script\");e.type=\"text/javascript\";e.onload=function(){var d={},f=0;hljs._hb=function(b){b.removeAttribute(\"data-hljs\");var c=b.innerHTML;c in d?b.innerHTML=d[c]:(7<++f&&(d={},f=0),hljs.highlightBlock(b.firstChild),d[c]=b.innerHTML)};hljs._ha=function(){for(var b=document.querySelectorAll(\"pre[data-hljs]\"),c=b.length;0<c;)hljs._hb(b.item(--c))};hljs._ha()};e.async=!0;e.src=\"//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/highlight.js/9.7.0/highlight.min.js\";a.appendChild(e)}\n </script>\n</li>\n<li>\n 篩選發文日期區段：\n <pre data-hljs=\"\"><code class=\"language-text\"> 日期格式爲 YYYY-MM-DD\n created:&lt;開始日期&gt;..[結束日期]</code></pre>\n<script>\n if(\"undefined\"!==typeof hljs)hljs._ha();else if(\"undefined\"===typeof hljsLoading){hljsLoading=1;var a=document.getElementsByTagName(\"head\")[0],e=document.createElement(\"link\");e.type=\"text/css\";e.rel=\"stylesheet\";e.href=\"//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/highlight.js/9.7.0/styles/default.min.css\";a.appendChild(e);e=document.createElement(\"script\");e.type=\"text/javascript\";e.onload=function(){var d={},f=0;hljs._hb=function(b){b.removeAttribute(\"data-hljs\");var c=b.innerHTML;c in d?b.innerHTML=d[c]:(7<++f&&(d={},f=0),hljs.highlightBlock(b.firstChild),d[c]=b.innerHTML)};hljs._ha=function(){for(var b=document.querySelectorAll(\"pre[data-hljs]\"),c=b.length;0<c;)hljs._hb(b.item(--c))};hljs._ha()};e.async=!0;e.src=\"//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/highlight.js/9.7.0/highlight.min.js\";a.appendChild(e)}\n </script>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n 上述四個篩選條件均能自由組合，實例：\n </p>\n<pre data-hljs=\"\"><code class=\"language-text\"># 搜尋站長發的文，文章日期介於 2019-12-01 至 2019-12-31，並且只篩出還有某些樓層還沒看過的文章\nauthor:Z created:2019-12-01..2019-12-31 is:unread</code></pre>\n<script>\n if(\"undefined\"!==typeof hljs)hljs._ha();else if(\"undefined\"===typeof hljsLoading){hljsLoading=1;var a=document.getElementsByTagName(\"head\")[0],e=document.createElement(\"link\");e.type=\"text/css\";e.rel=\"stylesheet\";e.href=\"//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/highlight.js/9.7.0/styles/default.min.css\";a.appendChild(e);e=document.createElement(\"script\");e.type=\"text/javascript\";e.onload=function(){var d={},f=0;hljs._hb=function(b){b.removeAttribute(\"data-hljs\");var c=b.innerHTML;c in d?b.innerHTML=d[c]:(7<++f&&(d={},f=0),hljs.highlightBlock(b.firstChild),d[c]=b.innerHTML)};hljs._ha=function(){for(var b=document.querySelectorAll(\"pre[data-hljs]\"),c=b.length;0<c;)hljs._hb(b.item(--c))};hljs._ha()};e.async=!0;e.src=\"//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/highlight.js/9.7.0/highlight.min.js\";a.appendChild(e)}\n </script>\n<pre data-hljs=\"\"><code class=\"language-text\"># 站務等級以上偷窺無辜使用者：標題或內文含有「測試」，隱藏的文章\n# 如果只是普通會員就只能看到自己刪的文章\n測試 is:hidden</code></pre>\n<script>\n if(\"undefined\"!==typeof hljs)hljs._ha();else if(\"undefined\"===typeof hljsLoading){hljsLoading=1;var a=document.getElementsByTagName(\"head\")[0],e=document.createElement(\"link\");e.type=\"text/css\";e.rel=\"stylesheet\";e.href=\"//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/highlight.js/9.7.0/styles/default.min.css\";a.appendChild(e);e=document.createElement(\"script\");e.type=\"text/javascript\";e.onload=function(){var d={},f=0;hljs._hb=function(b){b.removeAttribute(\"data-hljs\");var c=b.innerHTML;c in d?b.innerHTML=d[c]:(7<++f&&(d={},f=0),hljs.highlightBlock(b.firstChild),d[c]=b.innerHTML)};hljs._ha=function(){for(var b=document.querySelectorAll(\"pre[data-hljs]\"),c=b.length;0<c;)hljs._hb(b.item(--c))};hljs._ha()};e.async=!0;e.src=\"//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/highlight.js/9.7.0/highlight.min.js\";a.appendChild(e)}\n </script>\n<p>\n 實例截圖我就不放了，有興趣請自行測試。\n </p>\n<p>\n 但是要注意的是，由於上述篩選條件都包含英文，而目前卡特搜尋英文會爆炸，所以如果想用這個功能的話，強烈建議\n <strong>\n 先在別的地方把整串文字組合好後再複製過來\n </strong>\n ，而不是直接在搜尋框一字一字鍵入\n <br/>\n （卡特的搜尋是每次內容變動就觸發，這樣搞一定出事）\n </p>\n<p>\n 最後，有些組合就是死活搜不到，那不是你打錯，是卡特本身的搜尋就不完善。\n </p>\n<hr/>\n<p>\n 參考：\n </p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/flarum/core/blob/d492579638fb52dafbfe65f1f36a95eb6047f7f3/src/Discussion/Search/Gambit/HiddenGambit.php#L22\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">\n is:hidden\n </a>\n</li>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/flarum/core/blob/d492579638fb52dafbfe65f1f36a95eb6047f7f3/src/Discussion/Search/Gambit/UnreadGambit.php#L23\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">\n is:unread\n </a>\n</li>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/flarum/core/blob/d492579638fb52dafbfe65f1f36a95eb6047f7f3/src/Discussion/Search/Gambit/CreatedGambit.php#L22\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">\n created:\n </a>\n</li>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/flarum/core/blob/d492579638fb52dafbfe65f1f36a95eb6047f7f3/src/Discussion/Search/Gambit/AuthorGambit.php#L23\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">\n author:\n </a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n"}, {"author": "可惡想成為大佬", "body": "\n<p>\n 大佬…\n </p>\n"}, {"author": "可可蘿的頭號大粉絲", "body": "\n<p>\n 佬…我後來都用google直接搜\n </p>\n"}, {"author": "天涯之外", "body": "\n<p>\n<a class=\"PostMention\" data-id=\"691021\" href=\"https://kater.me/d/62880/3\">\n 可可蘿的頭號大粉絲\n </a>\n<br/>\n 我也是習慣用 Google 搜，只不過湊巧看到這四個功能\n <br/>\n 搭配「祕笈」廢文風潮，挺合適的\n </p>\n"}, {"author": "可可蘿的頭號大粉絲", "body": "\n<p>\n<a class=\"PostMention\" data-id=\"691025\" href=\"https://kater.me/d/62880/4\">\n 天涯之外\n </a>\n<br/>\n 這個秘笈比我的實用多了吧…\n </p>\n"}, {"author": "天涯之外", "body": "\n<p>\n<a class=\"PostMention\" data-id=\"691027\" href=\"https://kater.me/d/62880/5\">\n 可可蘿的頭號大粉絲\n </a>\n 我覺得沒有。原因有二\n </p>\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:decimal\">\n<li>\n 卡特目前搜尋不夠完備，很多關鍵字會意料外地搜不出結果\n </li>\n<li>\n 這四個參數比較適合自動化，或許由紅色扳手加入快速篩選的功能就會超級棒ㄌ\n </li>\n</ol>\n"}, {"author": "Fruit丨vinegar", "body": "\n<p>\n 很實用\n </p>\n"}, {"author": "katerであるグループに審判された359番号だ", "body": "\n<p>\n 都看無\n </p>\n"}, {"author": "天涯之外", "body": "\n<p>\n<a class=\"PostMention\" data-id=\"691052\" href=\"https://kater.me/d/62880/8\">\n katerであるグループに審判された359番号だ\n </a>\n 沒關係 這只是篇廢文\n </p>\n"}, {"author": "青霧島響", "body": "\n<p>\n 哈哈是這個啦\n </p>\n"}, {"author": "天涯之外", "body": "\n<p>\n<a class=\"PostMention\" data-id=\"795919\" href=\"https://kater.me/d/62880/10\">\n 青霧島響\n </a>\n 喔喔，所以你是手打關鍵字嗎？\n </p>\n"}, {"author": "青霧島響", "body": "\n<p>\n<a class=\"PostMention\" data-id=\"795928\" href=\"https://kater.me/d/62880/11\">\n 天涯之外\n </a>\n<br/>\n 沒 一篇一篇看\n </p>\n"}, {"author": "天涯之外", "body": "\n<p>\n<a class=\"PostMention\" data-id=\"795948\" href=\"https://kater.me/d/62880/12\">\n 青霧島響\n </a>\n 更怪物，你是不是一天有 48 小時\n </p>\n"}, {"author": "青霧島響", "body": "\n<p>\n<a class=\"PostMention\" data-id=\"795955\" href=\"https://kater.me/d/62880/13\">\n 天涯之外\n </a>\n<br/>\n 沒有 期末快爆了\n </p>\n"}, {"author": "天涯之外", "body": "\n<p>\n<a class=\"PostMention\" data-id=\"795967\" href=\"https://kater.me/d/62880/14\">\n 青霧島響\n </a>\n 快去讀…\n </p>\n"}, {"author": "青霧島響", "body": "\n<p>\n<a class=\"PostMention\" data-id=\"795972\" href=\"https://kater.me/d/62880/15\">\n 天涯之外\n </a>\n<br/>\n 好…\n </p>\n"}, {"author": "青霧島響", "body": "\n<p>\n 不過我記得還有一篇是用腳本考古鉀金屬\n <br/>\n 但沒找到就是了\n </p>\n"}, {"author": "天涯之外", "body": "\n<p>\n<a class=\"PostMention\" data-id=\"796121\" href=\"https://kater.me/d/62880/17\">\n 青霧島響\n </a>\n 你是說這個嗎？\n </p>\n<p>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/dsxsrst.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/dsxsrsth.jpg\" title=\"\"/>\n</a>\n</p>\n"}, {"author": "青霧島響", "body": "\n<p>\n<a cl